race.comment: WHISKEY WHISKERS (1) was quickly out of the boxes with a slick early sectional clocking 25.84 with a one length win at Geelong over 460m. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. OFF THE CHART (5) charged out of the boxes with a fast early split and led throughout to score when a 2 length winner (24.88) over 450m at Shepparton. The form out of last race has been strong. Hard to fault the current string of winning form and can continue his winning ways. TREBLE BEERS (2) can keep up the top recent form following a solid 30.09 win two back with a Restricted WIN H victory at Warrnambool over 450m in 25.34. Flying lately and shapes as a definite danger again. CACO MAGIC (7) bold run expected on best form.
